  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "Let's play soccer - the world's favorite sport!\n\nIn Super Soccer you can choose between an Exhibition mode and a Tournament mode. While the first mode lasts a single game only the Tournament mode challenges you with 16 consecutive games, facing the Nintendo Allstar Team in the final round.\n\nThe field is shown in a top-down perspective. Scrolling is done by Mode 7 chip. Difficulty varies with the opponent team, ranging from easy to hard in later games in the tournament.\n\nAfter winning a match in the tournament mode, you will be rewarded witch a code in order to pick up the game in the same round of the tournament later on.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
